This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to detect temporal relations between events. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves the use of weakly supervised learning, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves the use of information retrieval techniques, which falls under the category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper also involves the use of domain-specific knowledge, which falls under the category of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
